the dangerous usiraqi standoff in the desert rattled nerves 
across the middle east 
israel fired off a test missile as a warning to the iraqis air 
raid sirens wailed mysteriously in jordan turkish villagers said 
iraqi tanks had rumbled into position near the turkeyiraq border 
and iraq closed its frontiers for foreigners heightening concerns 
about hundreds of americans stranded in iraq and kuwait 
