states vast property for decades private property has been 
illegal in this communist state but gorbachev has been moving 
toward it as part of his economic reforms 
tass said the new fund would organize transformation of state 
enterprises into joint stock societies and other new arrangements 
its goals include breaking up state monopolies in production 
protecting state property and carrying out measures to privatize 
property tass said 
