say 
lt gen charles a horner 53 was named thursday to head 
desert shield the us military effort to prevent further iraqi 
advances in the persian gulf 
hes the forward commander hes the one thats on the ground 
and out in the boonies directing the show said one pentagon 
officer 
the threestar general a native of davenport iowa has lived 
here since 1987 with wife mary jo he commands the 9th air force 
and the us central command air forces at nearby shaw air force 
base 
friends in sumter a city of 29000 about 45 miles from 
