so what you are seeing is a reaction of anger at the united 
states he said 
it is not that the palestinians support the regime in iraq or 
believe in saddam husseins ideology but because they believe 
there is a double standard in the area husseini said 
husseini spent a year of the uprising in jail without trial on 
