stopped iraqis clearly were unsettled by the prospect reports 
filtering out of the isolated nation told of panicky people 
hoarding rice cooking oil and other foodstuffs 
up to 50000 us troops are expected to pour into saudi arabia 
in the coming weeks in operation desert shield as it has been 
dubbed pentagon sources say contingency plans call for as many as 
250000 to be sent depending on whether a grave iraqi threat 
develops 
