charge stemming from the fbi sting operation in the fbi videotape 
barry was seen smoking crack cocaine with former girlfriend 
rasheeda moore at the vista hotel on jan 18 juror johnnie mae 
hardeman said the panel deadlocked 66 on the charge arising from 
that night 
the single cocaine possession conviction carries a maximum 
penalty of one year in jail and a 100000 fine 
